iterations.yara_rule:
rule Bypass_Sample
{
    meta:
        description = "Evasion bypass rule"
        cape_options = "bp0=$pattern0+0,action0=skip,bp1=$pattern1+0,action1=skip,bp2=$pattern2+0,action2=skip,count=0"

    strings:
        $pattern0 = { 8D B0 74 0C 00 00 56 56 50 50 E8 44 09 00 00 }  //LEA + PUSH + CALL (Option 4)
        $pattern1 = { 55 8B EC 8B 45 08 8B 88 14 0A 00 00 56 6A 36 } //PUSH + MOV + MOV (Option 5)
        $pattern2 = { 6A 35 5A 8B CE E8 44 09 00 00 85 C0 } //PUSH + POP + MOV + CALL (Option 6)

    condition:
        any of them
}
